my family
There are 6 of us my dad's the  oldest my mum's the second oldest
my oldest sister is 22 and married with 1 child of 3 months
my second sister is 18 and she worked for the mobile blood-transfusion centre she has a flat at Michems corner Tonbury my third sister is 16 and works at the milk company Tonbury and shares the flat with my other sister
I live at Elmden on a farm As I am the youngest person in the family I get picked on for a lot of things here is a EG
when we are all watching TV
dad says make a cup of tea mum
mum says Doris you make a cup of tea
