the car went straight through a brick wall and turned over four times in the road then it went on fire
there was no hope of peter and Jane coming out of the car alive
when the people heard the bang they came running out to see what they could do but it was too late for anything to be done they were both dead
peter's left leg was missing and Jane was burned all over
a man rang for the police and ambulance when they came the crowd was told to go home and don't worry about the crash
the next their parents was told of their sudden death
then they flew the bodies over to england to be buried there near their parent's home too two days after the funeral took place peter's mother fainted over the grave of her son the coffins were put one on top of the other in the grave peter's mother had to be carried away by her other son and husband who were both crying with heartbreak Jane's mother was unable to attend the funeral because she was ill after she had heard the shock
after the funeral they all went home weeping
it was three weeks when peter and jane got married and as they were going on honeymoon peter's dad said for a joke don't kill yourself after six weeks had gone they still kept on taking about their daughter and son
and not long after that peter's mother died with heart attack , so then peter's family was the loneliest family in the world peter's dad tried to stop him from crying but it was no use
now they were dead and nothing could be done at all
peter's father took his son for a holiday to Italy
then they soon got over the shock but it took a long while peter's father never went near a car since the death of his son and daughter in law
THE END

