Poor Bob
It is ten years since Bob had his accident he was a bright lad I shall never forget when I and Bob fell into a river coming home from church on Sunday night we had got our clothes on
The were covered with mud and wet right through, when we got home mother and father nearly killed us and then that night when we were all in bed, bob saw a lorry come up the road he always liked lorries and cars he got up without a sound and hurried down stairs and opened the door and ran out into the road in front of the lorry it killed him straight out he was only seventeen years old when he was killed
I am just going to put some more flowers on his grave are you coming with me
The End

