She did not know the police will ask her what have you got in that basket " "I have some dirty washing I am going to take them to the laundry
" What is that shuffling in that basket "nothing sir" nothing "let me have a look please " "no you can not" " you're not going to see what I own no you're not" "I can hear a baby cry "that is not your baby" "you stole it" The lady started to run as fast as she could the policeman blew his whistle the other policemen came and started to run after her She did not get very far before the policeman caught up with her she struggled a bit but they calmed her down and took her to the police station she made a a statement and she was in jail for two years for killing babies
and the lady whose baby was stolen got her baby back safely

