My family I live in Melton and I am in a cottage and it is horrible we don't like it but still we have to Persevere till we leave
Bernard is ill in bed and the Doctor is coming to see him on Wednesday Morning he felt sick on the football ground on Saturday afternoon
Our dog Toby has been Excited but it's a very cute dog
I have got a bunk which I sleep in
my brother has a single bed and my mother and father has one too
we he haven't any cats but we used to do we used to have round about 12 but they all disappeared
I should think we will be leaving some time my Mother will be glad when we do leave this cottage we all do we don't know about the dog it might be different for him because he is used to that but never mind he will get used to that as well
We all want to go where our Relatons but my mother doesn't want to go to Leiston but I do I like it very much
I don't now know about my father and my brother but I know that they would like it
There are six in my family counting the dog and the bird
we have a garden and it has only grass on each side Well on the left of the garden was a hole in the middle and there was mice in it down the bottom of it
Well one of the cats meant to go outside but something happens he sees this hole and he puts his paw into the hole and the mice come up a little and they grabbed the cat
then it tried to get away but it was no use it was killed then they all came out and then they all were killed
Then there was my mother and father and I came out of the house that night and saw that the cats were in the hole making a noise but we couldn't do anything about it because it was too late
But have got over it

